dex.name: Sword, Shield
dex.selection_rule:
(p.variantForm === null
    or p.variantForm?.name in ['Alternate', 'Gender', 'Therian']
)
and (
    p.regionalForm === null
    or p.regionalForm?.name in ['Alolan', 'Galarian']
)
and (
    p.specialForm === null
    or p.specialForm?.name === 'Gigantamax'
)
and ba?.swordshield
and p.name not in ['Dialga-Origin', 'Palkia-Origin']
dex.description:
The list of obtainable Pokémons in Sword and Shield games, as well as the DLC "Isle of Armor" and "Crown Tundra"

These versions do not contain all existing Pokémons.

Gigamax forms appear in the games for certain ancient (Blastoise or Butterfree) or new (Corviknight or Drednaw) Pokémons.
dex.french_description:
La liste des pokémons obtenable dans les jeux Épée et Bouclier, ainsi que les DLC "L'île solitaire de l'Armure" et "Les terres enneigées de la Couronne"

Ces versions ne contiennent pas tous les pokémons existants. 

Les formes Gigamax apparaissent dans le jeux pour certains pokémons anciens (Tortank ou Papilusion) ou nouveaux (Corvaillus ou Torgamord).
